   {
      "body" : "Per-tx events are going to average at least once per second.  For this patch -- yuck -- you are continually running new OS processes.  It is far more efficient to combine stock bitcoind with https://github.com/jgarzik/pynode/tree/mini-node if you simply want to see all transactions that are accepted (and relayed) by bitcoind.\r\n\r\nTherefore this patch and polling are both the wrong solutions IMO.",
